@graph.schema:name: Data-Centric Security. Letting information defend itself from… | by Kevin Doubleday | Fluree PBC | Medium
@graph.schema:description: What is Data-Centric Security? The Data-Centric philosophy involves moving data management responsibilities from the application tier to the data tier — and security is no exception.
